title: The Presets - Apocalypso 2008 V0 [MP3,LOG]
description:
Apocalypso is the second full length album by Australian electronic duo The Presets. The album was released by Modular Recordings on the 8th April 2008 in Australia and will feature the singles "My People" and "This Boy&#039;s In Love". "My People" featured in the 2007 Triple J Hottest 100, where it placed at number 18.
